displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.
Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: “Manike (From "Thank God")” by Yohani, Jubin Nautiyal, Tanishk Bagchi, Rashmi Virag, and Surya Ragunaathan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 58 spots at #38.
“DOABA” by Garry Sandhu and Jind Dhillon is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #53.
Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. “The Last Ride” is the highest at #7.
“Excuses” by AP Dhillon, Gurinder Gill, and Intense has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 51 weeks straight.
